    "q_en": "<p>If '+' means '&#215;', '&#8211;' means '&#247;', '&#215;' means '+' and '&#247;' means '&#8211;', what will come in place of the question mark (?) in the following equation?<br><br>18 + 15 &#215; 580 &#8211; 29 &#247; 22 = ?</p>",
